What do you mean by &quot;mass add&quot;? To what are you adding these tests? If 
it&#39;s an IDE or command-line project (built by Ant or Maven), check the 
build tool&#39;s documentation for how to run tests. For example, in Ant, 
the &lt;junit&gt; target has a &lt;batchtest&gt; element that allows you to specify 
test names using wildcards, such as

&lt;junit&gt;
   &lt;batchtest todir=&quot;test-logs/&quot;&gt;
     &lt;fileset dir=&quot;test-src/&quot;&gt;
       &lt;include name=&quot;**/*Test*.class&quot;/&gt;
     &lt;/fileset&gt;
   &lt;/batchtest&gt;
&lt;/junit&gt;

